metadata.name: New Winter 2023
metadata.description:
Happy New Year 2023 in Enoshima  
_____ 
If you purchase NFT art of my collection, you may use it in the following ways  
●For collection.  
●For use within the range of personal use. (e.g., use it as wallpaper for your smartphone or PC, print it out and hang it in your room, etc.)  
●For use as a profile or header image on a social networking service, or share it in a post.  
● For exhibiting NFTs in virtual galleries such as Oncyber, where they can be displayed.  
*Please contact us if you wish to exhibit in a physical exhibition (non-virtual exhibition) or use the NFT in ways other than those listed above.
